{"tid":1444302,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人，你地準備好背水一戰未？","createTime":"2019-08-11T12:04:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T02:42:01.000Z","uid":61106,"like":99,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5a9fc00c5a7ac1404a58f26e38122a75f9aa01","tid":1444302,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:04:34.000Z","msg":"經過埋今日，如果你地仲係無決心背水一戰，咁不如放棄呢場運動啦，唔好再要人為你受傷。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，係時候要背水一戰！"},{"pid":"cc4ff5c7916a36851590894996784f73228262e3","tid":1444302,"uid":232817,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:04:50.000Z","msg":"重返金鐘，正面開拖"},{"pid":"4e4be264189a1432459a6b0b859a2e081069a2b7","tid":1444302,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"78ae87a09226dc6b064dce7ebfa5487cfd50d5da","tid":1444302,"uid":61106,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:25.000Z","msg":"我地要救番被捕人士"},{"pid":"a6b5bce76908fe54252eef8c95f7be8f905ee68c","tid":1444302,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:06:49.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"b46b22a1f439deefea8479aecf54b47a2d42c8a6","tid":1444302,"uid":61106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:07:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f2f38f68ef931b3aef5b5d571d01dd74a8054333","tid":1444302,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:09:01.000Z","msg":"真係要醒啦"},{"pid":"fa4fcf56e81b7995cf49380ed12e89d0ba844059","tid":1444302,"uid":61106,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:10:15.000Z","msg":"推撚到光復香港"},{"pid":"ba9cf864a4636907d781112638afe385377e4b1b","tid":1444302,"uid":202137,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T12:11:07.000Z","msg"